::KitKat::

"CRIPES!!! Megatron, Pardon me, I'll be right back."
She ordered her clone to come with her. "Destructor, Help me with 
this one."

She transformed into wolf mode, her clone just ran along side her in 
bot mode. She ran down to the lab and saw th hole inthe floor. "That 
little fox, when I get my teeth on him...." She turned adn ran after 
him. She could hear the sond of Drillbit's gun. She was getting close.
